Package com.powerbi.api.controller

package com.powerbi.api.controller
This package contains controllers for the application. Controllers handle HTTP requests and provide endpoints for managing various entities such as channels, links, and users. Each controller is responsible for a specific domain and interacts with the corresponding service layer to process requests.
